  "name": "metro",
  "description": "Five-substation metro grid with TWIN FEEDERS. SUB-X is outaged: X1 is a solo double-ring feeder on CB-X1, while X2 and X3 are a TWIN PAIR sharing CB-X23 (one breaker to a shared riser XR-23 that splits to both feeder heads), so X2 and X3 lose supply together. On the healthy side SUB-A's A1 and A2 are likewise a twin pair on CB-A12. SUB-B/C/D feeders are solo. Seven tie paths, parallel ties into X2, undersized ties forcing sectionalizing splits and partial shed.",
